<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel vakna haw cheng cheng sanga,
 Vakzaw leh lopi zaw;
 Isu chuh ka vakna ahi,
 Ka lunggil ah a vak.

[V2]
 Aw vak deihum chuh a vak hi,
 Lungmuonna, kipahna a hung tung;
 Isu kipah mel ka muh in,
 Ka lunggil a kipak hi.

[V3]
 2. Ka lunggil ah thil gihawih a um,
 Ka Lalpen pakna la;
 La ka sakdawk theih loh cheng le,
 Isu'n A za thei hi.

[V4]
 3. Lunggil ah chavang kawlni bang eng,
 Lalpa ahung naih tieng;
 Ka lunggil ah muonna a um,
 Lungsietna pak a lang.

[V5]
 4. Lawpna, kinepna leh hehpihna,
 Ka lunggil ah a um;
 Chunglam a kipahna um leh,
 Ei vangsakna ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>SUNSHINE IN THE SOUL</title>
<hymn_number>321</hymn_number>
</song>